00037 void DataSetUpdaterTest::CreateReferenceFile()
00038 {
00039         // Create the data object.
00040         GenericData data;
00041         data.Header().SetFilename(TEST_FILE);
00042 
00043         DataGroupHeader dgHdr(L"data");
00044         DataSetHeader dsHdr;
00045 
00046         dsHdr.SetName(L"test");
00047         dsHdr.AddAsciiColumn(L"string8", 64);
00048         dsHdr.AddUnicodeColumn(L"string16", 64);
00049         dsHdr.AddByteColumn(L"int8");
00050         dsHdr.AddShortColumn(L"int16");
00051         dsHdr.AddIntColumn(L"int32");
00052         dsHdr.AddUByteColumn(L"uint8");
00053         dsHdr.AddUShortColumn(L"uint16");
00054         dsHdr.AddUIntColumn(L"uint32");
00055         dsHdr.AddFloatColumn(L"float");
00056         dsHdr.SetRowCnt(3);
00057 
00058         dgHdr.AddDataSetHdr(dsHdr);
00059 
00060         data.Header().AddDataGroupHdr(dgHdr);
00061         data.Header().GetGenericDataHdr()->SetFileTypeId("affymetrix.test.data");
00062 
00063 
00064 
00065         // Write the data object to the file
00066         GenericFileWriter writer(&data.Header());
00067         writer.WriteHeader();
00068 
00069         DataGroupWriter &dataGroupWriter = writer.GetDataGroupWriter(0);
00070         dataGroupWriter.WriteHeader();
00071 
00072         //int iSet=0;
00073         DataSetWriterIt beginSet;
00074         DataSetWriterIt endSet;
00075         dataGroupWriter.GetDataSetWriters(beginSet, endSet);
00076 
00077         beginSet->WriteHeader();
00078 
00079         int32_t dataSetSz = beginSet->GetDataSetSize();
00080         int32_t offset = writer.GetFilePos();
00081         writer.SeekFromCurrentPos(dataSetSz + 1);
00082         beginSet->UpdateNextDataSetOffset();
00083 
00084         dataGroupWriter.UpdateNextDataGroupPos();
00085         
00086         writer.SeekFromBeginPos(offset);
00087 
00088 
00089         // Write the data.
00090         beginSet->Write("first_row", 64);
00091         beginSet->Write(L"first_row", 64);
00092         beginSet->Write((int8_t) 1);
00093         beginSet->Write((int16_t) 1);
00094         beginSet->Write((int32_t) 1);
00095         beginSet->Write((u_int8_t) 1);
00096         beginSet->Write((u_int16_t) 1);
00097         beginSet->Write((u_int32_t) 1);
00098         beginSet->Write(1.0f);
00099 
00100         beginSet->Write("second_row", 64);
00101         beginSet->Write(L"second_row", 64);
00102         beginSet->Write((int8_t) 2);
00103         beginSet->Write((int16_t) 2);
00104         beginSet->Write((int32_t) 2);
00105         beginSet->Write((u_int8_t) 2);
00106         beginSet->Write((u_int16_t) 2);
00107         beginSet->Write((u_int32_t) 2);
00108         beginSet->Write(2.0f);
00109 
00110         beginSet->Write("third_row", 64);
00111         beginSet->Write(L"third_row", 64);
00112         beginSet->Write((int8_t) 3);
